nodes.text: Corellian red was a type of wine. In 22 BBY, Corellian red was being served at the Outlander Club on the planet Coruscant and was kept in a tall tube on the counter behind the club's central bar. It was a favorite among smugglers, pilots and shipbuilders and was served in Oga's Cantina in Black Spire Outpost on Batuu.
